        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Python爬虫学习之路（1）"><a href="#Python爬虫学习之路（1）" class="headerlink" title="Python爬虫学习之路（1）"></a>Python爬虫学习之路（1）</h1><h2 id="爬取我的博客主页面的源代码"><a href="#爬取我的博客主页面的源代码" class="headerlink" title="爬取我的博客主页面的源代码"></a>爬取我的博客主页面的源代码</h2><hr><h2 id="1-向发送服务器发送请求"><a href="#1-向发送服务器发送请求" class="headerlink" title="1.向发送服务器发送请求"></a>1.向发送服务器发送请求</h2><p>要获取网页中的相关信息，首先应当向服务器发送一个<code>request</code>。<br>导入<code>^request</code>包以使用该功能： </p><pre><code class="Python"><span class="keyword">import</span> request</code></pre><hr><h2 id="2-使用get-方法获取网页信息"><a href="#2-使用get-方法获取网页信息" class="headerlink" title="2.使用get()方法获取网页信息"></a>2.使用get()方法获取网页信息</h2><pre><code class="Python">url = <span class="string">'https://golden-pigeon.github.io/'</span>strhtml = requests.get(url)//strhtml储存了网页的信息</code></pre><hr><h2 id="3-输出网页源代码"><a href="#3-输出网页源代码" class="headerlink" title="3.输出网页源代码"></a>3.输出网页源代码</h2><p><code>strhtml</code>对象的<code>text</code>成员储存了网页的源代码<br>用<code>print()</code>函数将其输出即可  </p><pre><code class="Python">t=strhtml.textprint(t)</code></pre><hr><h2 id="4-完整程序"><a href="#4-完整程序" class="headerlink" title="4.完整程序"></a>4.完整程序</h2><pre><code class="Python"><span class="keyword">import</span> requestsurl = <span class="string">'https://golden-pigeon.github.io/'</span>strhtml = requests.get(url)t=strhtml.textprint(t)</code></pre><hr><h2 id="5-输出"><a href="#5-输出" class="headerlink" title="5.输出"></a>5.输出</h2><pre><code class="HTML"> <span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"zh_CN"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span>  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>Hexo<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"viewport"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"width=device-width, initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no"</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"author"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"John Doe"</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">property</span>=<span class="string">"og:type"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"website"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">property</span>=<span class="string">"og:title"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"Hexo"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">property</span>=<span class="string">"og:url"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"http:&amp;#x2F;&amp;#x2F;yoursite.com&amp;#x2F;index.html"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">property</span>=<span class="string">"og:site_name"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"Hexo"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">property</span>=<span class="string">"og:locale"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"zh_CN"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">property</span>=<span class="string">"article:author"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"John Doe"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"twitter:card"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"summary"</span>&gt;</span>    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">"alternative"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/atom.xml"</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"Hexo"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"application/atom+xml"</span>&gt;</span>//后略</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
